---
import Page from "../Page.astro";

interface Props {
  totalPages: number;
  tabLabel?: string;
}
const { totalPages, tabLabel } = Astro.props;
---

<Page pageNumber={6} totalPages={totalPages} tabLabel={tabLabel}>
  <Fragment slot="front">
    <div class="h-full relative flex flex-col pt-0">
      <div class="absolute top-0 right-0 w-full flex justify-center"></div>

      <div class="mb-3 md:mb-4 min-h-[60px]">
        <h2 class="text-2xl md:text-3xl font-serif font-bold text-primary mb-1">
          Sérénité Plus
        </h2>
        <p
          class="text-xs md:text-sm font-poppins italic text-dark/60 mb-2 md:mb-3 leading-relaxed"
        >
          L’accompagnement continu pour un site vivant.
        </p>
        <div class="h-1 w-12 bg-primary/40"></div>
      </div>
      <p class="font-sans text-[14px] text-dark/70 leading-relaxed mb-4">
        Avoir un site est une chose. Avoir un site qui reste vivant, sécurisé et
        fluide au quotidien en est une autre. Et c’est précisément ce qui
        transforme l’expérience — pour vous comme pour les personnes qui vous
        découvrent.
      </p>

      <p class="font-sans text-[14px] text-dark/70 leading-relaxed mb-4">
        <strong>Sérénité Plus</strong> est un accompagnement continu, conçu pour vous
        offrir une tranquillité d’esprit durable.
      </p>

      <div
        class="p-6 md:p-10 rounded-2xl md:rounded-[2.5rem] border border-zinc-100 bg-highlight/30 relative overflow-hidden flex-1 flex flex-col shadow-sm"
      >
        <div class="mb-6 md:mb-8">
          <div class="text-2xl md:text-3xl font-serif font-bold text-dark mb-1">
            150 €
          </div>
        </div>

        <ul
          class="space-y-2 md:space-y-3 mb-8 md:mb-10 flex-grow text-[12px] md:text-[14px]"
        >
          <li
            class="flex items-start gap-3 md:gap-4 text-dark/80 font-sans leading-relaxed"
          >
            <div
              class="w-5 h-5 md:w-6 md:h-6 rounded-full flex items-center justify-center text-secondary bg-white/80 shrink-0 mt-0.5 shadow-sm"
            >
              <svg
                xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg"
                viewBox="0 0 24 24"
                fill="none"
                stroke="currentColor"
                stroke-width="3"
                stroke-linecap="round"
                stroke-linejoin="round"
                class="w-3 h-3 md:w-3.5 md:h-3.5 lucide lucide-check"
                ><path d="M20 6 9 17l-5-5"></path></svg
              >
            </div>
            <span>Hébergement managé premium</span>
          </li>
          <li
            class="flex items-start gap-3 md:gap-4 text-dark/80 font-sans leading-relaxed"
          >
            <div
              class="w-5 h-5 md:w-6 md:h-6 rounded-full flex items-center justify-center text-secondary bg-white/80 shrink-0 mt-0.5 shadow-sm"
            >
              <svg
                xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg"
                viewBox="0 0 24 24"
                fill="none"
                stroke="currentColor"
                stroke-width="3"
                stroke-linecap="round"
                stroke-linejoin="round"
                class="w-3 h-3 md:w-3.5 md:h-3.5 lucide lucide-check"
                ><path d="M20 6 9 17l-5-5"></path></svg
              >
            </div>
            <span>Sauvegardes quotidiennes</span>
          </li>
          <li
            class="flex items-start gap-3 md:gap-4 text-dark/80 font-sans leading-relaxed"
          >
            <div
              class="w-5 h-5 md:w-6 md:h-6 rounded-full flex items-center justify-center text-secondary bg-white/80 shrink-0 mt-0.5 shadow-sm"
            >
              <svg
                xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg"
                viewBox="0 0 24 24"
                fill="none"
                stroke="currentColor"
                stroke-width="3"
                stroke-linecap="round"
                stroke-linejoin="round"
                class="w-3 h-3 md:w-3.5 md:h-3.5 lucide lucide-check"
                ><path d="M20 6 9 17l-5-5"></path></svg
              >
            </div>
            <span>Mises à jour & sécurité</span>
          </li>
          <li
            class="flex items-start gap-3 md:gap-4 text-dark/80 font-sans leading-relaxed"
          >
            <div
              class="w-5 h-5 md:w-6 md:h-6 rounded-full flex items-center justify-center text-secondary bg-white/80 shrink-0 mt-0.5 shadow-sm"
            >
              <svg
                xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg"
                viewBox="0 0 24 24"
                fill="none"
                stroke="currentColor"
                stroke-width="3"
                stroke-linecap="round"
                stroke-linejoin="round"
                class="w-3 h-3 md:w-3.5 md:h-3.5 lucide lucide-check"
                ><path d="M20 6 9 17l-5-5"></path></svg
              >
            </div>
            <span>30 min de retouches mensuelles</span>
          </li>
          <li
            class="flex items-start gap-3 md:gap-4 text-dark/80 font-sans leading-relaxed"
          >
            <div
              class="w-5 h-5 md:w-6 md:h-6 rounded-full flex items-center justify-center text-secondary bg-white/80 shrink-0 mt-0.5 shadow-sm"
            >
              <svg
                xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg"
                viewBox="0 0 24 24"
                fill="none"
                stroke="currentColor"
                stroke-width="3"
                stroke-linecap="round"
                stroke-linejoin="round"
                class="w-3 h-3 md:w-3.5 md:h-3.5 lucide lucide-check"
                ><path d="M20 6 9 17l-5-5"></path></svg
              >
            </div>
            <span>Rapport de performance</span>
          </li>
        </ul>

        <button
          type="button"
          onclick="window.goToContact()"
          class="w-full py-3 md:py-5 rounded-2xl font-bold text-[10px] md:text-xs uppercase tracking-widest transition-all font-sans bg-primary text-white hover:bg-primary/90 shadow-lg shadow-primary/10 transform hover:-translate-y-0.5 cursor-pointer block text-center"
        >
          Me contacter
        </button>
      </div>
    </div>
  </Fragment>
  <Fragment slot="back">
    <div class="h-full flex flex-col">
      <div class="mb-8 min-h-[60px] back-divider-right">
        <h2 class="text-3xl font-serif font-bold text-primary mb-2">
          Portfolio
        </h2>
        <div class="h-1 w-16 bg-primary"></div>
      </div>

      <div class="flex-grow flex flex-col justify-center">
        <div class="p-5 md:p-8 rounded-2xl md:rounded-[2.5rem] bg-highlight/30 border border-highlight relative overflow-hidden w-full">
          <p class="font-sans text-[12px] md:text-[14px] text-dark/80 leading-relaxed mb-4">
            Découvrez une sélection de projets façonnés avec exigence, intention et sens du détail.
          </p>
          <p class="font-sans text-[12px] md:text-[14px] text-dark/80 leading-relaxed mb-4">
            Chaque création reflète ma vision du design : des identités fortes, des interfaces maîtrisées et des expériences digitales pensées pour durer.
          </p>
          <p class="font-sans text-[12px] md:text-[14px] text-dark/80 leading-relaxed">
            Un portfolio qui met en lumière la précision, la cohérence et l’esthétique qui guident mon travail au quotidien.
          </p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </Fragment>
</Page>
